'''Canto VII. G<U+012B>tas<U+012B>t<U+0101>svaya<U+1E43>varopakrama<U+1E25>'''  (Sanskrit: <U+0917><U+0940><U+0924><U+0938><U+0940><U+0924><U+093E><U+0938><U+094D><U+0935><U+092F><U+0902><U+0935><U+0930><U+094B><U+092A><U+0915><U+094D><U+0930><U+092E><U+0903>), literally ''the canto with the songs of the commencement of S<U+012B>t<U+0101>'s Svaya<U+1E43>vara''.

'''Canto VIII. G<U+012B>tas<U+012B>t<U+0101>n<U+012B>ketaka<U+1E25>''' (Sanskrit: <U+0917><U+0940><U+0924><U+0938><U+0940><U+0924><U+093E><U+0928><U+093F><U+0915><U+0947><U+0924><U+0915><U+0903>), literally ''the canto with the songs of S<U+012B>t<U+0101>'s consort''.

'''Canto IX. G<U+012B>tas<U+012B>t<U+0101>svaya<U+1E43>vara<U+1E25>''' (Sanskrit: <U+0917><U+0940><U+0924><U+0938><U+0940><U+0924><U+093E><U+0938><U+094D><U+0935><U+092F><U+0902><U+0935><U+0930><U+0903>), literally ''the canto with the songs of S<U+012B>t<U+0101>'s Svaya<U+1E43>vara''.

'''Canto X. G<U+012B>tas<U+012B>t<U+0101>r<U+0101>mapari<U+1E47>aya<U+1E25>''' (Sanskrit: <U+0917><U+0940><U+0924><U+0938><U+0940><U+0924><U+093E><U+0930><U+093E><U+092E><U+092A><U+0930><U+093F><U+0923><U+092F><U+0903>), literally ''the canto with the songs of the S<U+012B>t<U+0101>'s marriage with R<U+0101>ma''.

'''Canto XI. G<U+012B>tas<U+012B>t<U+0101>r<U+0101>mapratyudgamotsava<U+1E25>''' (Sanskrit: <U+0917><U+0940><U+0924><U+0938><U+0940><U+0924><U+093E><U+0930><U+093E><U+092E><U+092A><U+094D><U+0930><U+0924><U+094D><U+092F><U+0941><U+0926><U+094D><U+0917><U+092E><U+094B><U+0924><U+094D><U+0938><U+0935><U+0903>), literally ''the canto with the songs of the festivities at the return of S<U+012B>t<U+0101> and R<U+0101>ma''.

